Package io.github.randomcodespace.container.strategy

Class PodmanStrategy

java.lang.Object
io.github.randomcodespace.container.strategy.AbstractCliStrategy
io.github.randomcodespace.container.strategy.PodmanStrategy
All Implemented Interfaces:
ContainerManager, ImageManager, ContainerToolStrategy
public class PodmanStrategy extends AbstractCliStrategy
Strategy for interacting with Podman. For MVP, this will primarily use CLI interactions. API interaction (Libpod or Compat) would be a more advanced implementation.

      options - Options for fetching logs (e.g., follow, tail).
